info:
The aim of this node is to format the data recevied from "DataService Read Variables" node, in order to create and save a CSV file with all the datapoints extracted from the Data Service database.

The CSV file format will be the following:

|timestamp|VarA|VarB|...|VarC|
|.........|....|....|...|....|
|.........|....|....|...|....|
|.........|....|....|...|....|

name: write to file
info: Save a CSV with filename **csvdataextract.csv** containing all the datapoints extracted from Data Service application.
